==Dialogue==
{{Dialogue Start}}
:<!--Trigger PerformanceE 504110001: Config/Level/Mission/5041100/Act/Act504110001.json-->
:'''Hieronymus:''' Oh? It's you. Not every day a guest shows up in this village &mdash; Nice field, huh?
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Did you plant all this wheat yourself?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504110003-->
::'''Hieronymus:''' Hahaha, not a chance! A field this size? If I had to tend it solo, I'd collapse from exhaustion.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} It's a beautiful wheat field.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504110005-->
::'''Hieronymus:''' I know, right? The crop's looking fantastic this year. Look at that golden hue, doesn't it outshine {{Rubi|Mnestia|Romantic Titan}}'s dress?
:<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_504110006-->
:<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504110006-->
:'''Hieronymus:''' You're one of us now, no need to be shy. With such fine weather, once our grapes have fermented, be sure to take my kids out to the wheat fields. Sit in the sun, feel the breeze... I'm not bragging, it feels great.
:<!--Ends the current performance-->
{{Dialogue End}}
